      <title>Michelle Obama &amp; Jon Batiste Play The Piano | American Symphony | Netflix</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<img align="right" hspace="5" src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ff9HEuGK-UM/hqdefault.jpg"/>Love, music, the healing power of art… and a little bit of piano magic with Michelle Obama and Jon Batiste 🎹 🎶 American Symphony is now playing on Netflix.<br/><br/>➡️Watch on Netflix: <a href="https://www.netflix.com/title/81728930" target="_blank">https://www.netflix.com/title/81728930</a><br/><br/>About Netflix:<br/>Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.<br/><br/>Michelle Obama & Jon Batiste Play The Piano | American Symphony | Netflix<br/><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@stillwatchingnetflix" target="_blank">https://www.youtube.com/@stillwatchingnetflix</a><br/><br/>In this deeply intimate documentary, musician Jon Batiste attempts to compose a symphony as his wife, writer Suleika Jaouad, undergoes cancer treatment.]]></description>
